      "description": "color - Allow the magnet to affect the point color of the input geometry.\t\nTip: To control the contribution of each magnet on the surface's  Color when the Affect  Color option is enabled, set your point colors to black (0,0,0) before the Magnet  by using a Point SOP. The Translate fields in the Magnet  will then add per-point rgb color with values of 2,2,2 approaching white. \t\t\t\nThe scale and rotate channels of the magnet move you about in 3D color space. This is not recommended.",
